    This chapter serves as 'Update No. 1' to a July 2024 report, providing a concise overview of significant global developments in humanoid robotics, particularly from late 2024 through early 2025. It emphasizes that rapid advancements in AI are making the mass production of smart humanoids technologically feasible, positioning them as a multi-tasking force multiplier across various sectors, from industry and services to home and security. The report h...
