    This report provides a concise update on the rapidly evolving global humanoid robotics landscape, detailing significant developments since July 2024. It emphasizes the field's strong growth, propelled by advancements in AI, positioning humanoids as versatile, multi-tasking force multipliers across industry, services, and domestic applications. The period under review showcases consistent progress, new model launches, and an expanding technological a...
